<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A brown tree snake constitutes nonmailable matter under <ref href="/us/usc/t39/s3015">section 3015 of title 39</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf03ba4d4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/384/s6">Pub. L. 108–384, § 6</ref>, <date date="2004-10-30">Oct. 30, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/2224">118 Stat. 2224</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
